The paper deals with statistical modeling and machine learning techniques for automatic estimation of piano fingering. This involves constructing hidden Markov models and deep neural networks to describe the naturalness of a given fingering in terms of probabilities. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category for this paper is cs.SD (Sound), followed by cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.SI (Social and Information Networks), and cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction).
